{"type": "article", "id": 22695, "title": "煮鸡蛋小工具", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-23T07:30:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 53, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115131KRmBnbQr3ZeAFfxk.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一个帮助煮鸡蛋的小工具，来自以色列设计师 Shahar Nissim 和以色列一家专门供应奇妙的产品的公司 monkey business 一起推出。它是用耐高温和耐水性好的硅胶材料做的，可以随着鸡蛋一起在锅里煮，手提的圆环除了控制移动，还可以帮助鸡蛋站立在桌面上，像是蒙上了一个忍者面具。有黑色和红色两种，售价 15 美元，<a href=\"http://www.mnkbusiness.com/egg-ninjas/\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115129QuNVLqBh3A4pR7nd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115129FMpN2m5zgo6Rfdb3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115130IAjU1wkcJbPL5W9R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115130Cnfj4vlU2MRr73W5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55501222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115130vaVmg31jSFqu4JoM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}